ergirl R|{{abbr|S|Supergirl}}]] {{*}} [[#Batwoman R|{{abbr|B|Batwoman}}]] \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[Emiko Queen (Arrowverse)|Emiko Queen <br/><small> Green Arrow</small>]]\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|Sea Shimooka{{note label|main|M|}}\n|Sea Shimooka\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[Mia Smoak|Mia Smoak <br/><small>Blackstar / Green Arrow</small>]]\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|colspan=\"1\" | [[Katherine McNamara]]\n|colspan=\"1\" | Katherine McNamara{{note label|main|M|}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" |  [[#Supergirl R|{{abbr|S|Supergirl}}]] {{*}}  [[#Batwoman R|{{abbr|B|Batwoman}}]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"10\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" scope=\"row\" |\n\n=== {{anchor|Arrow R}} Introduced in other series ===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Jim Corrigan]]\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|[[Stephen Lobo]]\n| rowspan=\"24\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Ryan Choi (Arrowverse)|Ryan Choi]]\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|[[Osric Chau]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[William Clayton (Arrowverse)|William Clayton]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| colspan=\"3\" | Jack Moore<ref name=\"Dilip\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/arrow-season-4-episode-19-air-date-spoilers-laurels-death-fake-canary-cry-set-photos-reveal-674482 |title='Arrow' Season 4 episode 19 air date, spoilers: Laurel's death fake, 'Canary Cry' set photos reveal who really is in the grave |last=Dilip |first=Mangala |date=April 13, 2016 |publisher=[[International Business Times]] |access-date=April 23, 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424054535/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/arrow-season-4-episode-19-air-date-spoilers-laurels-death-fake-canary-cry-set-photos-reveal-674482 |archivedate=April 24, 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=htt