 the main cast for the season.\n* A {{note label|universe|U|}} indicates the actor was in the season as an \"Arrowverse regular\".\n* A {{note label|Voice|V|}} indicates a voice-only role.\n* A number beside a character's name indicates the character is from that alternate world (i.e. a {{note label|Earth-2|2}} indicates a character from Earth-2).\n* A letter in the Further series column indicates the character has gone on to appear in another series, and links to the appropriate section for more information (A links to ''Arrow'', V links to ''Vixen'', S links to the ''Supergirl'', and L links to ''Legends of Tomorrow'').\n</blockquote>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\"  <!--The percentages on series must add to make 75% so that the columns are the same size-->| [[The Flash (season 1)|Season 1<br /><small>(2014\u201315)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\" | [[The Flash (season 2)|Season 2<br /><small>(2015\u201316)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\" | [[The Flash (season 3)|Season 3<br /><small>(2016\u201317)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\" | [[The Flash (season 4)|Season 4<br /><small>(2017-18)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\" | [[The Flash (season 5)|Season 5<br /><small>(2018-19)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:12.5%;\" | [[The Flash (season 6)|Season 6<br /><small>(2019-20)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" | Further series\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" |\n\n===Introduced in season 1===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Gorilla Grodd (Arrowverse)|Grodd]]\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[David Sobolov]]{{note label|Voice|V|}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://screencrush.com/flash-grodd-return-2017-david-sobolov/ |title=Gorilla Grodd Is Returning to 'The Flash' in 2017 |work=ScreenCrush.com |date=December 29, 2016 |accessdate=March 7, 2017 |first=Kevin |last=Fitzpatrick }}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|David Sobolov{{n