h{{note label|main|M|}} \n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Kara<br /><small>Overgirl</small>{{note label|Earth-X|X}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| Melissa Benoist\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | [[#Arrow R|{{abbr|A|Arrow}}]] {{*}} [[#The Flash R|{{abbr|F|The Flash}}]] {{*}} [[#Legends of Tomorrow R|{{abbr|L|Legends of Tomorrow}}]] {{*}} [[#Freedom Fighters R|{{abbr|FF|Freedom Fighters}}]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Oliver<br /><small>Dark Arrow</small>{{note label|Earth-X|X}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| Stephen Amell\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | [[#Arrow R|{{abbr|A|Arrow}}]] {{*}} [[#The Flash R|{{abbr|F|The Flash}}]] {{*}} [[#Legends of Tomorrow R|{{abbr|L|Legends of Tomorrow}}]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Nora West-Allen<br /><small>XS</small>\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| Jessica Parker Kennedy<ref name=\"Kennedy\" /><ref name=\"KennedyRole\" />\n| colspan=\"2\"style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | [[#The Flash R|{{abbr|F|The Flash}}]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" scope=\"row\" |\n\n===Introduced in season 4===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Lois Lane\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| colspan=\"2\"| Elizabeth Tulloch\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" |[[List of Arrowverse cast members#The Flash R|<abbr>F</abbr>]] &nbsp;\u2022 &nbsp;[[List of Arrowverse cast members#Legends of Tomorrow R|<abbr>L</abbr>]]{{*}}[[#Batwoman R|{{abbr|B|Batwoman}}]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[Agent Liberty|Ben Lockwood <br /><small> Agent Liberty</small>]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| [[Sam Witwer]]{{note label|main|M|}}\n| Sam Witwer\n| style=\"backgroun