ay:table; margin: 0;\">\n'''{{center|List indicator(s)}}'''\n* This table includes main cast members, as well as notable guest stars that appear across two different ''series''.\n* A dark grey cell indicates the character was not in the season, or that the character's presence in the season has not yet been announced.\n* An {{note label|main|M|}} indicates the actor was part of the main cast for the season.\n* A {{note label|universe|U|}} indicates the actor was in the season as an \"Arrowverse regular\".\n* A {{note label|Voice|V|}} indicates a voice-only role.\n* A number beside a character's name indicates the character is from that alternate world (i.e. a {{note label|Earth-2|2}} indicates a character from Earth-2).\n* A letter in the Further series column indicates the character has gone on to appear in another series, and links to the appropriate section for more information (A links to ''Arrow'', F links to ''The Flash'', and S links to the ''Supergirl'').\n</blockquote>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:15%;\"  <!--The percentages on series must add to make 75% so that the columns are the same size-->| [[Legends of Tomorrow (season 1)|Season 1<br /><small>(2016)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Legends of Tomorrow (season 2)|Season 2<br /><small>(2016\u201317)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Legends of Tomorrow (season 3)|Season 3<br /><small>(2017-18)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Legends of Tomorrow (season 4)|Season 4<br /><small>(2018-19)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Legends of Tomorrow (season 5)|Season 5<br /><small>(2020)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" | Further series\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" |\n\n===Introduced in season 1===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Connor Hawke (Arrowverse Earth-16)|John Diggle, Jr.<br><small>Connor Hawke / Green Arrow</small>]]\n| [[Joseph David-Jones]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http