ter|List indicator(s)}}'''\n* This table includes main cast members, as well as notable guest stars that appear across two different ''series''.\n* A dark grey cell indicates the character was not in the season, or that the character's presence in the season has not yet been announced.\n* An {{note label|main|M|}} indicates the actor was part of the main cast for the season.\n* A number beside a character's name indicates the character is from that alternate world (i.e. a {{note label|Earth-38|38}} indicates a character from Earth-38).\n* A letter in the Further series column indicates the character has gone on to appear in another series, and links to the appropriate section for more information (A links to ''Arrow'', F links to ''The Flash'', L links to ''Legends of Tomorrow'', and FF links to ''Freedom Fighters'').\n</blockquote>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Supergirl (season 1)|Season 1<br /><small>(2015\u201316)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Supergirl (season 2)|Season 2<br /><small>(2016\u201317)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Supergirl (season 3)|Season 3<br /><small>(2017-18)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Supergirl (season 4)|Season 4<br /><small>(2018-19)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | [[Supergirl (season 5)|Season 5<br /><small>(2019-20)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" | Further series\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" |\n\n===Introduced in season 1===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Alex Danvers \n| colspan=\"5\" | Chyler Leigh{{note label|main|M|}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | [[#Arrow R|{{abbr|A|Arrow}}]] {{*}} [[#The Flash R|{{abbr|F|The Flash}}]] {{*}} [[#Legends of Tomorrow R|{{abbr|L|Legends of Tomorrow}}]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Kara Danvers<br /><small>Supergirl</small> \n| colspan=\"5\" | Melissa Benoist{{note label|main|M|}}\n| style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | [[#Arrow R|{{